@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam stateFontSize 11

title Digital Asset Lifecycle

[*] --> Stored : Upload\n(POST /upload)

Stored : Asset persisted in database
Stored : Bytes, Name, ContentType set
Stored : Height/Width extracted (images)

Stored --> Stored : Serve\n(GET /serve/{id})
Stored --> Stored : Update\n(re-upload same name)
Stored --> Stored : Batch Retrieve\n(GET /range)

Stored --> Deleted : Delete\n(DELETE /{id})

Deleted : Record removed from database
Deleted : DigitalAssetDeletedEvent published

Deleted --> [*]

@enduml
